Hi, Harry.

647
01:03:03,277 --> 01:03:04,476
Hi.

648
01:03:04,478 --> 01:03:06,213
Hiding in the playroom, are we?

649
01:03:06,215 --> 01:03:07,847
Yes.

650
01:03:07,849 --> 01:03:09,849
Don't worry.

651
01:03:09,851 --> 01:03:11,953
I-I'm getting off
at the next stop.

652
01:03:13,255 --> 01:03:14,454
Going far?

653
01:03:14,456 --> 01:03:15,856
Bergen.

654
01:03:15,858 --> 01:03:17,958
Ah, rather you than me.

655
01:03:17,960 --> 01:03:20,994
