666
01:03:51,260 --> 01:03:52,528
Splendid.

667
01:03:54,096 --> 01:03:57,967
So, you...
you canceled the Oleg thing.

668
01:04:00,534 --> 01:04:02,401
The school trip.

669
01:04:02,403 --> 01:04:04,271
Weren't you supposed to...

670
01:04:04,273 --> 01:04:06,375
Oh, shit.

