674
01:04:15,550 --> 01:04:17,583
Shit.

675
01:04:17,585 --> 01:04:21,189
Look, look, you're-you're not
his father, Harry.

676
01:04:22,590 --> 01:04:25,592
- What does that mean?
- Well, uh...

677
01:04:25,594 --> 01:04:27,927
I don't have to be his father
