678
01:04:27,929 --> 01:04:29,329
I was trying to say that...

679
01:04:29,331 --> 01:04:30,930
it's a big enough
responsibility

680
01:04:30,932 --> 01:04:33,266
for a real father, isn't it?

681
01:04:33,268 --> 01:04:34,971
Let alone you and me.

682
01:04:36,972 --> 01:04:39,442
- Sorry, Harry.
