so I...

694
01:05:13,208 --> 01:05:16,108
No, it-it's totally
my fault, Oleg.

695
01:05:16,110 --> 01:05:19,045
Yes, yes. I'm sorry.

696
01:05:19,047 --> 01:05:21,182
I'm sorry, Oleg. Yes.

697
01:05:22,317 --> 01:05:23,650
Yeah.

698
01:05:23,652 --> 01:05:26,251
So, see... see you
in a few days, then,

699
01:05:26,253 --> 01:05:29,125
wh-when I'm back
from the conference. Yeah.

700
01:05:32,626 --> 01:05:34,663
You didn't have to do that.

701
01:06:19,173 --> 01:06:21,307
Ready? That's it!

702
01:06:21,309 --> 01:06:23,175
Stop!

703
01:06:23,177 --> 01:06:25,647
Hey, Aasen, someone here
to speak to you.

704
01:06:30,284 --> 01:06:32,020
Aasen.

705
01:06:37,458 --> 01:06:39,525
My family owned all
of these buildings.

706
01:06:39,527 --> 01:06:41,693
And that house over there, too.

707
01:06:41,695 --> 01:06:44,097
Arve Stop worked
for us back then.

708
01:06:44,099 --> 01:06:48,101
He was, uh, bright, ambitious.

709
01:06:48,103 --> 01:06:50,773
My father really
believed in him.

710
01:06:52,507 --> 01:06:54,307
The business
wasn't going very well,

711
01:06:54,309 --> 01:06:56,575
so we, uh, offered him a stake.

712
01:06:56,577 --> 01:06:59,813
Within a year,
he had forced us out.

713
01:06:59,815 --> 01:07:02,351
Sold the land for a fortune.

714
01:07:04,351 --> 01:07:08,220
Have any of my colleagues been
in touch with you recently?

715
01:07:08,222 --> 01:07:09,789
A young lady?

716
01:07:09,791 --> 01:07:11,291
No.

717
01:07:11,293 --> 01:07:14,626
I look at this picture now,

718
01:07:14,628 --> 01:07:17,333
I see Laila staring at him.

719
01:07:18,833 --> 01:07:20,802
No idea at the time.

720
01:07:22,670 --> 01:07:25,040
Family man, eh?

721
01:07:27,708 --> 01:07:31,177
Do you remember the name
of your wife's doctor?

722
01:07:31,179 --> 01:07:32,412
Sure.

723
01:07:32,414 --> 01:07:33,582
Uh, Morton Freiberg.

724
01:07:37,652 --> 01:07:42,222
Did she ever see someone
called Vetlesen?

725
01:07:42,224 --> 01:07:44,557
Vetlesen? No.

726
01:07:44,559 --> 01:07:46,195
Dr. Idar Vetlesen.

727
01:07:49,764 --> 01:07:51,367
No.

728
01:07:52,467 --> 01:07:54,467
Any idea where I might find

729
01:07:54,469 --> 01:07:56,802
