Am I under arrest?

736
01:09:00,435 --> 01:09:02,468
- A cake!
- Yeah.

737
01:09:02,470 --> 01:09:04,903
I need some information
on a patient.

738
01:09:04,905 --> 01:09:06,839
Laila Aasen.

739
01:09:06,841 --> 01:09:09,275
No, I don't... Listen to me.

740
01:09:09,277 --> 01:09:10,576
I don't know
the admitting doctor.

741
01:09:10,578 --> 01:09:12,544
