01:10:00,662 --> 01:10:02,829
He was a suicidal maniac.

761
01:10:02,831 --> 01:10:04,763
They were gonna
suspend him anyway.

762
01:10:04,765 --> 01:10:06,531
They found stuff
in his drawers.

763
01:10:06,533 --> 01:10:09,602
Items he'd stolen
