when he shot himself.

771
01:10:33,662 --> 01:10:35,831
What's this on the floor?

772
01:10:36,898 --> 01:10:40,299
They look like coffee beans.

773
01:10:40,301 --> 01:10:42,402
Maybe he was trying
to sober up after all.

774
01:10:44,773 --> 01:10:46,438
You didn't check?

775
01:10:46,440 --> 01:10:49,642
